<p>old front lines.  Fritz swept country very clean prior to evacuation. <br/>Arrived in Bapaume about 2.30 pm &amp; found the place practically demolished; majority of it being in flames.  Formed &amp; took charge of a relay post on the outskirts of the town &amp; chose a cellar as a place of abode.  Called out a few times during the night in the rain.</p>
